Fana viyandikile Maandiko Yelile, "Kwa ichimu cha weye wokomigwa siku zose, chila fana ng'hondolo wa kukomigwa."
Mbali muna yayo yose iyo, chochose chochimtenda yawe mkulu kufosa wagima kwa ija yoyatulondile.
