Na hebu udahi wa kuulanga, hebu ubanzi wa kuulanga, hebu chila chinhu chochose chiya chonda chizadaha kusegeza Mulungu yoyamulondile muna Chilisito Yesu Mndewa wetu.
Na niye nolonga ukweli muna Chilisito, siulonga uvwizi, na hakili zangu zonilagusa muna Muhe Yelile.
