Mbali Mulungu kamwidikaze choni? "Nihasiga wanhu magana malongo saba magana malongo mane hawamtumbalile kumwinamila Bahali."
Iviya, sambi bahabaho wanhu wamwenga wowasaguligwe na Mulungu kwa ubazi wake.
Mbali one wahasaguligwe kwa ubazi wa Mulungu, si kwa kutenda yanogile. One ihadahika kwa kutenda yanogile, uhasanyi haukalile ubazi wa Mulungu.
